  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nAnvil\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nSupport a custom RPC method called `eth_sendUncheckedTransaction` \r\n\r\noriginally from `taichi.network` works the same as `eth_sendRawTransaction`, but never checks the nonce or gas price of the transaction. This can be used to broadcast transactions with faster responses. You have to make sure that the transaction is valid ofc.\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\npart of https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/issues/2396",
